    Enclosing interface:
    MembershipOracle<I,D>

    public static interface MembershipOracle.MealyMembershipOracle<I,O>
extends MembershipOracle<I,net.automatalib.words.Word<O>>
    A specialization of the MembershipOracle that binds the output domain to Words of the specified output type. Queries should be answered according to the Mealy output semantics (transition-based). This means an input sequence of length n results in an output word of length n.
